  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icloud.com,General
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn-apple.com,General

  # Social media - 走容错链
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,twitter.com,General
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,x.com,General
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,facebook.com,General
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,instagram.com,General
